body:
Hello, 

You have to download the graph and label files as a zip file from [https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/inception5h.zip] and extract the contents to `~/graphs/inception/` folder since you are using the `--graph` flag as `--graph=~/graphs/inception/tensorflow_inception_graph.pb`.
